ActNational Capital Act
SubjectTRILLIUM BEVERAGES INC. Five year renewal options 555 Wellington Street
PrecisOrder authorizing the NATIONAL CAPITAL COMMISSION enter into a ten-year lease beginning no later than November 1st, 2010 and with three renewal options of 5 years each, with TRILLIUM BEVERAGES INC. operating as the Mill Street Brewery (Trillium) for a property located at 555 Wellington Street, in Ottawa.
